{"tid":170221,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［求解夢］夢見女朋友","createTime":"2017-03-24T15:13:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T17:11:16.000Z","uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73b54c7842849800b1584fa3bbab8d8f002cc121","tid":170221,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:13:00.000Z","msg":"琴晚發左個夢，到而家仲好深刻<br />\n<br />\n夢入面我搭緊地鐵，同一個朋友一齊，仲有一個女仔。個女仔我見都未見過，白白淨，長頭髮，冇帶眼鏡，稱唔上靚，斯斯文文咁。我地幾個有講有笑，但我明明唔識個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後發現夢入面個設定佢係我女朋友，但我明明就冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  後尾仲送埋佢返屋企<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢個咩夢黎？有冇咩特別含意？求連登解夢大師指點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14806fef0278d9fdae1456ee24ad40793d849826","tid":170221,"uid":5995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:13:40.000Z","msg":"平行世界姐"},{"pid":"afa0169094fb6c05533e277b7ecf7fc2e43a34bf","tid":170221,"uid":92769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:14:15.000Z","msg":"係時候要打丁啦"},{"pid":"12f19cfb93d22494d56306aebb8e46d09b335a59","tid":170221,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:15:15.000Z","msg":"夢就係夢，唔會有答案"},{"pid":"a674aaf5eab5b079b2bd3c074ea8b77780a8b85c","tid":170221,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>平行世界姐</blockquote><br />\n巴打信有平行世界？如果有我都想知另一個我過成點"},{"pid":"13b99661f722000ba87b5ef51ebc40a998b904ee","tid":170221,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:33:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係時候要打丁啦</blockquote><br />\n聖人mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最低限度都放低張j圖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1a33f70179761f077e4581cc7973fd7ac4a550","tid":170221,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夢就係夢，唔會有答案</blockquote><br />\n係今次好特別先討論下<br />\n明明係個素未謀面嘅人 點解我夢入面可以見得咁清楚 我覺得好神奇"},{"pid":"63670a84542cd3215c522b8bf80981c565a7f48a","tid":170221,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:36:42.000Z","msg":"幾次夢見有第三者添啦我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知真係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲特徵仲好似添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97b2d131fb5b4a5afc37c6f1f90f1d0a4c7982ac","tid":170221,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾次夢見有第三者添啦我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點知真係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲特徵仲好似添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會你本身都知道啲 懷疑緊？<br />\n巴打振作呀"},{"pid":"ab5aa1500bfee587614296d05e0e2d67a0103a22","tid":170221,"uid":92951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T16:59:35.000Z","msg":"講開又講<br />\n琴晚我發夢同一個中學同學拍拖<br />\n個夢仲好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係現實同呢個人完全唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n感覺好奇妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4caa5751fe798b3ceac7ccb185bba8ac64666784","tid":170221,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-24T17:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講開又講<br />\n琴晚我發夢同一個中學同學拍拖<br />\n個夢仲好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係現實同呢個人完全唔熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br /